title: 2115 - Timeless Sweats
description:
MATERIAL: 75% Cotton, 25% Polyester. Fleece.

FABRIC WEIGHT: 370 GSM.

FIT: Baggy.

DESIGN: The Timeless Sweats are designed for ultimate versatility, made to fit your style anytime, anywhere. Crafted from a comfortable 75% cotton and 25% polyester blend with a 370 GSM fabric weight, these sweats feature a sleek mesh panel on the sides for added breathability and style. The no-cuff bottom and printed logo give them a laid-back, athletic vibe that pairs well with any look.

MODEL: The model in the first photo is wearing a size Medium. Weight: 175lb Height: 5'9.
